在全屏应用中显示导航栏
在选定应用中显示导航栏

在一段时间后隐藏横条

自定义横条的行为方式
想知道如何使用该应用程序？我们在这里帮你

XDA 还有其他应用程序。看看他们!
通过付费插件解锁更多功能
adb shell pm grant com.xda.nobar android.permission.WRITE_SECURE_SETTINGS
该通知是为了阻止 Android 关闭本应用，长按进入设置隐藏它。
阻止横条移动到键盘前
某些设备在横向时，会在侧面显示原有的导航栏。激活此操作以防止该行为。
当上下颠倒时, 某些设备可以旋转屏幕, 将会导致原有的导航栏显示。请启用此选项以确保它保持隐藏状态。
许多平板电脑强制导航栏始终处于屏幕底部。打开此项可阻止该行为。
When enabled, the pill will automatically hide in fullscreen apps (e.g. videos or games).
不要更改这些选项, 除非您需要它们！它们可能导致问题, 而不是修复问题！
启用此选项可使横条更容易被滑动。
仅当设备具有虚拟导航栏时才可使用此功能。
启用后, 原有导航栏将可在全屏应用程序中通过上滑显示。
Set %s using pixel count rather than percentages.
将横条分成三部分，每个部分都有自己的一套动作。
启用后，导航手势将不会在车载模式下被禁用。请不要在具有虚拟导航栏的 TouchWiz 设备上启用此功能。
点按 \"确定\" 以允许导航手势写入系统设置。
分裂式横条已启用！是否尝试使用此模式的建议设置？
当激活隐藏导航栏时, 启用 Android 的沉浸式导航栏。这解决了三星设备的问题, 如 \"实体主页键\" 无法正常工作。
选择始终显示原有导航栏的应用。
选择哪些应用程序不显示横条。
选择哪些应用程序不使用沉浸模式。
启用后, 横条将在一定时间后自动隐藏。
禁用分裂式横条！是否要将受影响的设置变回默认值？
选择那些需要保留横条在最上层的应用，例如Facebook Messenger和Durpe等。
这些功能不完整, 可能无法在您的设备上使用!
默认情况下, 导航手势会使得1像素的原有导航栏可见。启用此项可减少该像素。警告: 这会破坏某些设备!!!
切换在屏幕上手势横条的开关。
切换虚拟导航栏的显示或隐藏。
启用此选项可显示锁定屏幕上的快捷方式。并修复在锁定屏幕、环境显示或始终显示时，图标只保留一部分的问题。
Certain devices (OnePlus) may have an issue where the \"Home\" action doesn\'t work. Enable this to use a workaround for that.

To help us debug Navigation Gestures, you can enable this option. By doing so, a random ID will be generated for you and associated with any crash logs we receive in Firebase. If you\'re having issues with the app crashing, simply describe the situation, and give us your ID. No need to capture your own logs.
EMUI\'s battery management has been known to cause issues with Navigation Gestures, breaking its functionality. We recommend disabling it for this app. The app name is Navigation Gestures.
TouchWiz\'s battery management has been known to cause issues with Navigation Gestures, breaking its functionality. We recommend disabling it for this app.
Enable the native navigation bar when the software keyboard is activated.
Play a sound when a gesture is performed.
Android has a built-in battery optimization feature, which tends to kill Navigation Gestures. Press the button below to disable optimizations for this app.
When enabled, the pill will stay anchored to the physical bottom of the device.
Enable this if having the flashlight toggle action assigned to a gesture breaks other flashlight toggles, such as Quick Settings.
My navigation bar doesn\'t hide in certain rotations.
My Galaxy device\'s force touch isn\'t working.
It\'s hard to hit the pill.
There\'s a white line at the bottom of my screen.
Check out the Settings for all the customization and troubleshooting options.
The pill isn\'t working in Facebook Chat Heads, Drupe, etc.
The pill overlaps with my screen content.
Navigation Gestures was unable to request a battery exemption on your device. We recommend disabling it manually.
My lock screen shortcuts are cut off.
If you can\'t find your solution in the Settings, open a new ticket on our support site.
The battery icon on my Pixel\'s Ambient Display is cut off.
Back up your current gesture settings to a file.
Restore gesture settings from a backup file.
Set the color of dividers to appear between the sections of the split pill.
When enabled, the pill will automatically fade to the specified opacity after the specified delay.
When enabled, the pill will automatically fade in fullscreen apps to the specified opacity after the specified delay.
The beta version of Navigation Gestures may have already fixed your issue. Give it a try!
Live on the bleeding edge with new features and improvements by signing up for the beta program.
Hide the beta sign-up button from the main screen.
The pill isn\'t showing on the lock screen, app permissions page, etc.
The native navigation bar keeps hiding itself after I toggle off \"Hide Navigation Bar\".
We use Firebase Analytics to help track crashes and other issues. We do not collect or share any personal data.
Disable the pill altogether when your device is on the lock screen.
Disable the pill altogether when you\'re adjusting an app\'s permissions.
Disable the pill altogether when you\'re sideloading an APK.
Show the pill in the native navigation area. Not compatible with the navigation bar hiding feature, nor devices without a software navigation bar.

While Navigation Gesture\'s accessibility service should keep the app running in most cases, certain devices still kill it. Enabling this should make Navigation Gestures run more reliably on these devices.
When \"Overlay NavBar\" is enabled, place a black bar behind it to hide the original navigation buttons.
We recommend that you restart Navigation Gestures after restoring your settings. Would you like to do so?
Sometimes, your best bet for fixing problems with Navigation Gestures is restarting the app. Tap here to give it a try.

On certain devices, when the pill is shown, attempting to perform actions on dialogs in specific apps will result in an \"Overlay Detected\" error. Use this option to hide the pill in selected apps when a dialog is shown.
这个应用程序为所有 Android 设备带来了惊人的导航手势。最好的是，它不需要root权限！在您可以使用手势之前，我们必须做一些事情来设置应用程序。
为了让导航手势显示手势横条，您需要授予权限，使其能够在其他应用上方显示。点击下面的按钮并操作。如果从Play Store中安装，则该权限已被授予。
此应用程序使用无障碍功能服务来模拟原有导航按钮。单击“授予”以启用访问权限。

Navigation Gestures needs WRITE_SECURE_SETTINGS for certain functions, such as hiding the navigation bar or toggling Battery Saver. Click the button below to learn how you can grant it. If you are rooted, accept the root prompt. You can skip this if you want, but features dependent on it will not function.\n\nNOTE: ADB is not root! It will not void your warranty, trip KNOX, etc.
您已经准备好使用导航手势了！您可以在以下页面或快速设置磁贴 (牛轧糖及更高版本) 中切换横条显示。
您已经准备好在该设备上使用导航手势了。
不用担心，您仍然可以使用该应用程序。Root权限会使设置更容易。如果您愿意，我们可以使用 root 访问权限自动授予此权限。否则，您可以选择使用教程/手动方法。
看起来像是一个或多个权限授权被拒绝了。不过不用担心，我们会帮你恢复正常工作的。
此操作需要高级版插件。您想购买它吗？
抱歉，此操作需要运行 Android 牛轧糖或更高版本的设备。
This action requires a device running Android Oreo or later. Sorry about that.
This action requires a device running Android Pie or later. Sorry about that.
Android 牛轧糖允许定制快速设置磁贴，我们提供了一个切换导航手势的开关。您可以通过从状态栏向下滑动两次，点击铅笔图标或 \"编辑\" ，之后拖动导航手势开关瓷砖到活动区域。
此应用程序使用无障碍功能服务来模拟导航按钮（如返回、主页和多任务按钮） 。我们不使用它来收集任何个人信息，也不会执行任何操作，除非用户自己操作。
因为你的设备版本为Android P，这个应用目前不一定支持该版本。
如果你通过该应用隐藏导航栏的话，在卸载导航手势之前,，请确保通过应用中的开关去显示虚拟导航栏！
使用这个应用,，你可能会发现在屏幕底部有一个白色的横条。这不是错误！这是为了防止出现更严重的问题，尤其是在 TouchWiz 设备上。
使用此应用时，如果您注意到原有导航栏仍然显示在不该显示的情况时，请从头到设置或是在兼容性中尝试兼容性选项。
您始终可以通过在该应用程序的主页面上的显示隐藏导航栏开关来重复此步骤。
导航手势无法在隐藏导航栏时使用此功能。
Unfortunately, there\'s no way to fix this. We can\'t make a dedicated navigation space for the pill. Try lowering the pill height or turning off Larger Hitbox in Behavior.

Navigation Gestures has crashed! Don\'t worry, we\'ve already got the information. If this happens often, consider enabling your Crashlytics ID and sending it to us. You can turn it on from the \"i\" button on the main screen of the app.
Unfortunately, on Android 5.0, and maybe some heavily customized versions of Android, there is no proper way to display the pill everywhere.
Set the pill color on a per-app basis. This overrides the color set in Appearance for apps you add.
Hi! I\'m here to make sure Navigation Gestures isn\'t killed. Hold down on me to disable this notification.
嗯，看来这个权限被拒绝了。请确保按照所有说明进行操作，然后重试。
横条隐藏了，点击或上滑使其重新显示。
找到 \"无障碍功能\" 并点击它。
卸载前，请确保 \"隐藏导航栏\" 已关闭！
Navigation Gestures is currently keeping your screen awake.
Please grant Navigation Gestures notification policy access.
